  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Transporter!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transporter is a platformer racing game. Choose among 3 types of vehicles: Classic, Amphibious and Military. Your goal is to preserve your goods, maintain balance, and overcome obstacles with at least one item left at the finish line.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transporter is a <strong>technical </strong>game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is necessary to slow down or speed up, maintain a good balance to preserve the goods, choose the best solution to overcome an obstacle, and select the optimal vehicle for the type of terrain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/631c43f3a864a4dace46f7287839aeee.poster.avif?t=1750748325\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/631c43f3a864a4dace46f7287839aeee.webm?t=1750748325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Worlds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transporter will be released with 2 worlds: <strong>Indy Jungle</strong> and <strong>Operation Overlord</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each world has its own specifics:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Indy Jungle</strong> will be well-suited for 4x4 vehicles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Operation Overlord</strong> is about war and you will have the most success with military vehicles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New worlds and vehicles will come as DLC later on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/a9c044fb4d1668cd66545fb6d0c1d068.avif?t=1750748325\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vehicles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 types of vehicles: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* <strong>Classic:</strong> good overall on all types of terrain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* <strong>Amphibious:</strong> faster on water.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* <strong>Military</strong>: armored and can shoot at obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and drive 19 different vehicles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/febf00f5c3fffb08d198b7bc70917a08.avif?t=1750748325\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Garage</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The garage allows you to change various settings on your vehicle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 main parameters: power, suspension, grip, brakes, fuel tank.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some vehicle-specific options: armor, handling, electromagnetism, ...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/955107dd95e13dc3369d4ef58a722766.avif?t=1750748325\" width=486 height=260 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Goods</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock 11 types of goods. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/7120455014df5591b7839bad907a68ef.avif?t=1750748325\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rankings</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transporter is a competitive game with a global ranking for each race.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/2fcc834b71edd263a200e0a6755fb25c.avif?t=1750748325\" width=487 height=339 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Transporter!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transporter is a platformer racing game. Choose among 3 types of vehicles: Classic, Amphibious and Military. Your goal is to preserve your goods, maintain balance, and overcome obstacles with at least one item left at the finish line.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transporter is a <strong>technical </strong>game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is necessary to slow down or speed up, maintain a good balance to preserve the goods, choose the best solution to overcome an obstacle, and select the optimal vehicle for the type of terrain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/631c43f3a864a4dace46f7287839aeee.poster.avif?t=1750748325\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/631c43f3a864a4dace46f7287839aeee.webm?t=1750748325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Worlds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transporter will be released with 2 worlds: <strong>Indy Jungle</strong> and <strong>Operation Overlord</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each world has its own specifics:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Indy Jungle</strong> will be well-suited for 4x4 vehicles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Operation Overlord</strong> is about war and you will have the most success with military vehicles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New worlds and vehicles will come as DLC later on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.st