lass=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887370/extras/2fcc834b71edd263a200e0a6755fb25c.avif?t=1750748325\" width=487 height=339 /></span></p>",
